---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Resources | LEGAL SKILLS">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <header class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-emerald-900 mb-4">Resources 📚</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-emerald-800/70">Master the tools of the future.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-6">New to Skills?</h2>
      <div class="solarpunk-card p-8">
        <p class="text-lg text-emerald-800/80 leading-relaxed">
          Everything you need to get started. Welcome to our comprehensive learning hub.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-6">What are Skills?</h2>
      <div class="solarpunk-card p-8">
        <p class="text-lg text-emerald-800/80 leading-relaxed">
          Learn what agent skills are and how they can supercharge your workflow. 
          A skill is a modular set of instructions that allows an AI to perform specific legal tasks...
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-6">Skills vs MCP</h2>
      <div class="solarpunk-card p-8">
        <p class="text-lg text-emerald-800/80 leading-relaxed">
          Understand the difference between skills and MCP servers. 
          One is about <strong class="text-emerald-700">action</strong>, the other is about <strong class="text-emerald-700">connection</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-6">Getting Started</h2>
      <div class="solarpunk-card p-8">
        <p class="text-lg text-emerald-800/80 leading-relaxed">
          Install your first skill in under 2 minutes. Follow our quick-start guide to get your first agent running.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-6">Create a Skill</h2>
      <div class="solarpunk-card p-8">
        <p class="text-lg text-emerald-800/80 leading-relaxed">
          Step-by-step guide to building and sharing your own skills. Join the community and contribute to the registry.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <a href="https://github.com/tuyo-ai/legal-skills" target="_blank" class="btn-primary inline-block">View GitHub Repo</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
